description:
Watch #Selfie documentary here: https://vimeo.com/ondemand/selfie
Get DVD here: https://www.littlelightstudios.tv/product/selfie/

Smart devices and social media are becoming ever present.  With this new discovery its time to ask ourselves some questions.  Are we growing more dependent upon being constantly plugged into the internet?  Does this obsession to share every detail make us clover to those we love or is it separating us from intimately building real relationships?  What guidance does the Bible give us to help us navigate through this ever increasing web of digital dependence?
